00:02:57,302 --> 00:03:00,221
WISHING TO MEET SOMEDAY

31
00:03:00,305 --> 00:03:02,182
A woman aged 52.

32
00:03:02,265 --> 00:03:04,934
She was admitted for hiccups
that went on for nearly 48 hours.

33
00:03:05,018 --> 00:03:07,937
Hiccups might seem harmless,
but what's important here is…

34
00:03:11,232 --> 00:03:13,151
that it went on for 48 hours.

35
00:03:13,234 --> 00:03:16,237
What can cause hiccups that last
longer than 48 hours,

36
00:03:16,321 --> 00:03:18,031
-Dr. Heo?
-Pardon?

37
00:03:19,324 --> 00:03:22,535
Normally, hiccups are caused
by irritated phrenic nerves

38
00:03:22,619 --> 00:03:27,081
