because he's busy.

58
00:04:28,393 --> 00:04:30,728
He never forgot once
in the past three months.

59
00:04:30,812 --> 00:04:32,772
There's no way it slipped his mind.

60
00:04:42,949 --> 00:04:44,325
Are you going to call his lab?

61
00:05:09,017 --> 00:05:10,101
DR. LEE YOO-JOON

62
