I have to go.

65
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:20,111
-Where are you going?
-To Dr. Cha? Right now?

66
00:05:20,194 --> 00:05:22,405
He's never been out of reach
like this before.

67
00:05:22,488 --> 00:05:24,324
He's at least been sending
an e-mail every day.

68
00:05:24,407 --> 00:05:26,284
Something must have happened.

