00:07:07,385 --> 00:07:08,344
Please.

74
00:07:10,471 --> 00:07:12,849
CALL ME AS SOON AS YOU'RE FINISHED
WITH YOUR PROJECT, PLEASE

75
00:07:17,812 --> 00:07:18,938
You're the only person

76
00:07:20,648 --> 00:07:22,442
that ever understood me.

77
00:07:24,986 --> 00:07:26,279
My illness

78
00:07:27,488 --> 00:07:28,448
and me as a person.

79
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:34,454
My world that was neither hot nor cold

80
00:07:36,998 --> 00:07:38,416
turned warm after I met you.

81
00:07:40,168 --> 00:07:42,503
Why didn't you give me an answer

82
00:07:42,587 --> 00:07:44,172
