280
00:27:28,521 --> 00:27:30,398
That brings back memories.

281
00:27:30,482 --> 00:27:33,401
In those days, I couldn't even
eat chicken breast freely.

282
00:27:33,485 --> 00:27:35,779
Now that he's been brought up,
should we really try?

283
00:27:36,404 --> 00:27:39,032
Try what? Can't we do anything on our own?

284
00:27:39,115 --> 00:27:40,408
We did fine until now!

285
00:27:41,451 --> 00:27:42,535
Right, Doctor?

286
00:27:42,619 --> 00:27:44,954
What? Yes, we did fine.

287
00:27:54,297 --> 00:27:55,340
What got into her?

