296
00:28:49,728 --> 00:28:51,771
-Congratulations.
-Thank you.

297
00:28:56,067 --> 00:28:57,777
ESTABLISHMENT AND MANAGEMENT PLANS

298
00:28:57,861 --> 00:28:59,446
OBJECTIVES AND SIGNIFICANCE OF THE CENTER

299
00:29:20,967 --> 00:29:23,595
You want to put together
