all normal too.

341
00:31:53,411 --> 00:31:55,038
I told you.

342
00:31:55,121 --> 00:31:58,124
All the tests I've done so far
came back normal.

343
00:31:59,500 --> 00:32:02,128
Do you believe what I say?

344
00:32:05,715 --> 00:32:07,342
Every hospital says

345
00:32:07,425 --> 00:32:10,094
