one of our professors said.

352
00:32:38,039 --> 00:32:39,290
"Remember this.

353
00:32:39,374 --> 00:32:43,002
The cause might be unknown,
but no pain is without a cause."

354
00:32:52,762 --> 00:32:54,847
I never know when my pain will come back.

