00:33:06,818 --> 00:33:07,819
That's what I pray.

359
00:33:09,445 --> 00:33:10,738
Doctor.

360
00:33:14,867 --> 00:33:16,536
Please set me free.

361
00:33:18,579 --> 00:33:19,455
I beg you.

362
00:33:24,293 --> 00:33:26,462
We'll do everything we can.

363
00:33:27,505 --> 00:33:28,756
Please hang in there.

364
00:33:32,135 --> 00:33:34,220
When you're done eating,
let's go do some more tests.

365
00:33:35,138 --> 00:33:36,222
Okay.

366
00:33:47,942 --> 00:33:49,027
What is it?

367
00:33:50,319 --> 00:33:52,739
It's all in English.
Are you good at English?

368
00:33:53,740 --> 00:33:56,534
It's from my friend, and I was going
to skip it because it's in English.

369
00:33:57,827 --> 00:34:00,705
But then I saw Dr. Cha's name right here.

370
00:34:02,040 --> 00:34:03,332
What is it even about?

371
00:34:06,753 --> 00:34:07,628
What is it?

372
00:34:23,269 --> 00:34:25,021
Come with me for a second.

