00:36:47,288 --> 00:36:49,498
I told you to tell me if you're sick.

404
00:36:50,499 --> 00:36:52,710
You were so sick that you almost died.

405
00:36:52,793 --> 00:36:54,420
Didn't you think of me?

406
00:36:56,297 --> 00:36:57,924
You could've died.

407
00:36:58,007 --> 00:37:00,176
How could you not even tell me?

408
00:37:00,760 --> 00:37:04,597
For three years, I was sure of nothing.

409
00:37:08,309 --> 00:37:09,393
My health,

410
00:37:11,145 --> 00:37:12,563
or the time I had left.

411
00:37:14,023 --> 00:37:15,024
But…

412
00:37:15,858 --> 00:37:17,652
I was sure of only one thing.

413
00:37:18,778 --> 00:37:22,365
I believed that our love
wouldn't end so easily.

414
00:37:25,576 --> 00:37:27,036
I didn't want to repeat that.

415
00:37:28,579 --> 00:37:32,750
When I recovered my health
and when I could convince you too,

416
00:37:35,878 --> 00:37:37,463
I wanted to return then.

417
00:37:40,549 --> 00:37:41,425
Sorry, Si-young.

418
00:37:43,928 --> 00:37:45,054
I'm sorry.

419
00:38:05,866 --> 00:38:06,701
But…

420
00:38:08,369 --> 00:38:10,621
