421
00:38:11,747 --> 00:38:12,623
Go to your patient.

422
00:38:13,291 --> 00:38:14,959
Go and do as I suggested.

423
00:38:15,042 --> 00:38:16,669
Monitor her brainwaves for 24 hours.

424
00:38:16,752 --> 00:38:17,628
