428
00:38:24,302 --> 00:38:26,929
After that, although
she remains conscious,

429
00:38:27,013 --> 00:38:29,098
she suddenly falls asleep.

430
00:38:29,181 --> 00:38:31,183
If no painkillers work on her,

431
00:38:31,267 --> 00:38:33,519
