438
00:38:47,950 --> 00:38:50,953
That's why painkillers and
digestive medicines didn't work.

439
00:38:51,037 --> 00:38:53,873
An anti-seizure drug
will work dramatically on her.

440
00:38:55,416 --> 00:38:56,417
It would.

