00:39:09,597 --> 00:39:11,057
-Dr. Cha!
-Dr. Cha!

442
00:39:11,140 --> 00:39:12,391
-Dr. Cha!
-Dr. Cha!

443
00:39:15,144 --> 00:39:17,646
How long has it been?
